text.tspan: THE BATTLE HYMN OF THE ERISTOCRACY
Mine brain has meditated on the spinning of the Chao;
It is hovering oer the table where the Chiefs
Gathered in discussion of the dropping of the Bomb;
She was not invited to the party that they held
So She threw a Golden Apple, stead of turnd
O it cracked the Holy Punchbowl and it made
* "Limbo Peak" refers to Old Limbo Peak, commonly called by the Greeks "Ol Limb Peak."
"The tide is turning... the enemy is suffering
